Phase: Sections
Input: Objectives SectionEnd Token
Options: control = brill

Rule:SubSec
(
({SectionEnd})
({Token.string == "-"})?
({Objectives})
({Token.string == ":"})?
({SectionEnd})
):Subsect
-->
:Subsect.ObjectivesHeading = {Rule = "SubSec", Heading = :Subsect@cleanString}

